Title:

Allow Customer Category Update for Referenced Applications

⸻

Description:

Currently, applications referenced in SPONSOR_APPLICATION_MAP cannot be edited, which prevents updating CUSTOMER_CATEGORY_ID.

Add a new button to allow updating only the CUSTOMER_CATEGORY_ID for a selected application, without enforcing the Sponsor_Application_Map reference validation.

⸻

Acceptance Criteria:
	•	New button available on Sponsor/Application Configuration screen.
	•	Allows updating CUSTOMER_CATEGORY_ID even if record exists in SPONSOR_APPLICATION_MAP.
	•	No other application fields are editable via this action.
	•	No reference validation error is shown.
	•	Update persists correctly in DB.

⸻

Short. Clear. No fluff.
